quests.desc: Hey, thanks for coming over to the TextWorld today, there is something I need you to do for me. First off, take a trip east. After that, venture north. And then, attempt to venture north. After that, move north. With that accomplished, try to venture west. With that done, attempt to move south. And then, move west. Then, make an effort to go to the south. Then, attempt to go to the east. That done, close the safe. That's it!

objective: I hope you're ready to go into rooms and interact with objects, because you've just entered TextWorld! First stop, go to the east. After that, make an attempt to head north. Next, take a trip north. Once you get around to doing that, move north. Then, travel west. Next, go to the south. If you can manage that, attempt to venture west. That done, try to venture south. Following that, attempt to go to the east. After that, make sure that the safe is closed. And once you've done that, you win!

main_quest.desc: I hope you're ready to go into rooms and interact with objects, because you've just entered TextWorld! First stop, go to the east. After that, make an attempt to head north. Next, take a trip north. Once you get around to doing that, move north. Then, travel west. Next, go to the south. If you can manage that, attempt to venture west. That done, try to venture south. Following that, attempt to go to the east. After that, make sure that the safe is closed. And once you've done that, you win!
